	* po/POTFILES.in: Added proxy-client.c, proxy-msg.c.
	* src/proxy-client.c, src/proxy-msg.c: Massaged error messages.
	* daemon/Makefile.am: Added zvbi-chains target.
	* src/Makefile.am: Added libzvbi-chains target.
